%% State Machine - Mermaid stateDiagram-v2
%% Convention:
%%   - [*] --> StateName : initial state
%%   - StateName --> [*] : final state
%%   - State name: NOUN of state (Active, Closed) - NOT verb (Activating)
%%   - Transition format: SourceState --> TargetState : event [guard] / action

stateDiagram-v2
  [*] --> Initial

  Initial --> Active : approve [credentials valid]
  Initial --> Rejected : reject [credentials invalid]

  Active --> Suspended : suspend [violation count > 3]
  Active --> Closed : close

  Suspended --> Active : reactivate / clearViolations()
  Suspended --> Closed : forceClose [grace period ended]

  Closed --> [*]
  Rejected --> [*]

